NG0144:1: rdo rje ging chen ka ta ra ging mchog bco brgyad la //
NG0144:2: bsgral ba'i rtsib ma bco brgyad mchod pa 'bul //
NG0144:3: ging chen thugs dam bskang ste dngos grub stsol //
NG0144:4: de nas zhal du bstabs pa 'di skad do //
NG0144:5: bstab po kha ram zhal phyes shing *//
NG0144:6: 'bar ba chen po zhal phyes shig /
NG0144:7: rnam rtog ma lus zhal du bstab //
NG0144:8: dbu dang phyag mang zhal phyes shig /
NG0144:9: dgra bgegs ma lus zhal du bstab //
NG0144:10: zhing gsol chas brgyad zhal phyes shig /
NG0144:11: bar du gcod pa zhal du bstab //
NG0144:12: sha za khrag 'thung zhal phyes shig /
NG0144:13: bsgral ba'i zhing bzhi zhal du bstab //
NG0144:14: rngam byed ma lus zhal phyes shig /
NG0144:15: bdud dang srin po bar gcod byed pa dang *//
NG0144:16: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgra rnams //
NG0144:17: ma lus bzhes te rol par mdzod //
NG0144:18: 'byung po'i khrag ni chang bas zhim //
NG0144:19: 'dod chags mchod pa bla na med //
NG0144:20: 'dod chags mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0144:21: gsung gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0144:22: 'byung po'i rus pa mar bas zhim //
NG0144:23: zhe sdang mchod pa bla na med //
NG0144:24: zhe sdang mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NG0144:25: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0144:26: 'byung po'i sha ni zan bas zhim //
NG0144:27: gti mug mchod pa bla na med //
NG0144:28: gti mug mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NG0144:29: sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0144:30: ma ha rak+ta ma ha mam sa ma ha kim ni ri ti kha ram kha hi /
NG0144:31: tshogs rgyud chen po rdzogs so //
NG0144:32: de nas gsang ba thabs dang shes rab byang chub
NG0144:33: sems kyi mchod pa la yang don rnam pa lnga
NG0144:34: ste // gzungs ma byin gyis brlab pa dang *//
NG0144:35: gnyis su med par sbyor ba dang *//
NG0144:36: gsang ba'i mkha' la sems can thams cad dbang bskur te gnas spar ba dang */
NG0144:37: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la byang chub sems kyi mchod pa 'bul ba dang */
NG0144:38: byang chub sems rdo rje'i lce yis dngos grub blang ba dang lnga'o //
NG0144:39: de la dang po gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NG0144:40: gzungs ma nyid yum shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i rang bzhin du /
NG0144:41: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa'i bzhugs gnas gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs la /
NG0144:42: gsang ba'i mkha' la dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshang bar gsal bar bsgom pa dang */
NG0144:43: gnas lngar yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lnga las /
NG0144:45: gsang ba'i yum bzhi'i bskor bar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NG0144:46: de nas gnyis su med par sbyor ba ni /
NG0144:47: dang po spyan gyis brda zhig mdzad de /
NG0144:49: mtshan mchog brgyan pa'i yum mchog shes rab spyan /
NG0144:50: shes rab don gyi brgyan pa'i thugs dam bskul /
NG0144:51: mi dmigs snying rje thams cad yongs la snyoms /
NG0144:52: thabs dang shes rab tshul khrims kyis /
NG0144:53: sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes bskul ba dang */
NG0144:54: yum gyis yab la 'di skad ces bskul lo //
NG0144:55: thabs la mkhas pa'i 'gro ba 'dren pa'i gtso //
NG0144:56: 'khor ba ma spangs gnas su dag pa la / @#//
NG0144:57: 'phags pa rnams la dgyes pa'i thugs dam bskul /
NG0144:58: bde ba chen po'i mchod pa rgyan du gzhes /
NG0144:59: sa ma ya hum zhes bskul bas /
NG0144:60: yab kyi phyag rgya chen po bzhis mnyam par sbyar /
NG0144:61: hum las gsang ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga par bsgom /
NG0144:62: rdo rje'i rwa lnga la rigs lnga'i snying po 'god /
NG0144:63: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad la yum gyi snying po 'god /
NG0144:64: pra be sha phat kyi sgo phyes /
NG0144:65: su ra to s+t+wam gyis bskul bas /
NG0144:66: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgyes pa gcig tu bltas te /
NG0144:67: mnyes pa chen po'i thugs dam bskang */
NG0144:69: rtags thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub bo //
NG0144:70: de nas gsang ba'i mkha' la sems can thams cad gnas spar te dbang bskur ba ni /
NG0144:71: nam mkhas gang nas gang du khyab par chos kyi dbyings kyis kyang gang nas gang du khyab par /
NG0144:72: yum gyi mkha' klong rnam par dag pas khyab pas /
NG0144:73: snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad yab yum gyi mkha'
NG0144:74: dbyings rnam par dag pa gzhal yas khang du gyur
NG0144:75: pa'i nang na // mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NG0144:76: cad kyi sems me mar rlung gis ma bskyod pa
NG0144:78: kun gzhi a'i rang bzhin dang */
NG0144:79: yid hum gi rang bzhin du bsdu /
NG0144:80: yum gyi mkha' la gnas pa de /
NG0144:81: yab yum 'od bsnol mar gtibs pas /
NG0144:82: a dang hum dang byang chub sems gsum du 'dres pa las /
NG0144:83: thams cad rdo rje sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i sras su gyur te /
NG0144:84: sems can thams cad rgyal ba'i sras su bzhengs /
NG0144:85: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyis kyang */
NG0144:86: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur te /
NG0144:87: sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'dzin cing byang chub sems kyi dbang byin te bzhag go /
NG0144:88: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la byang chub sems kyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NG0144:89: me long yu ba can gyi nang du bzhag la /
NG0144:90: srin mtheb kyis phyag rgyas gtso bo dang 'khor yan la mchod pa phul bas /
NG0144:91: dgyes pa chen po'i bdud rtsis mnyes nas /
NG0144:92: dngos grub stsol zhing byin gyis brlabs par mdzad pa'o //
NG0144:93: de nas byang chub kyi sems las rdo rje tshe'i dngos grub blang ba ni /
NG0144:94: dkyil 'khor lha thams cad yab yum gnyis su med
NG0144:95: par sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub kyi sems kun+da
NG0144:96: dkar tsa rar zag pas bdag gi byang chub kyi
NG0144:98: lce la blang nas tsit+ta la thim pas ye shes sems dpa'i sku tshon gang bar gyur te /
NG0144:99: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung du gyur to //
NG0144:101: tshogs kyi mchod pa phul ba'i le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NG0144:102: gyi phan pa dang yun gyi bde ba dang */
NG0144:103: // de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa'i grangs ni /
NG0144:104: rab kyis nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du dbul bar bya'o //
NG0144:105: 'bring gis dus bzhir dbul bar bya'o //
NG0144:106: thams mas kyang nyin lan re mtshan lan re dbul bar bya'o //
NG0144:107: de ci'i phyir zhe na spyad thang re zhig grol thang re dang */
NG0144:109: pa'i mchog re re 'grub par gsungs so //
NG0144:110: de la tshogs kyi mchod pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NG0144:111: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar /
NG0144:112: dka' ba da ltar spyad nas 'bras bu phyis 'ong du re ba ma yin te /
NG0144:113: tshogs kyi 'bras bu ni yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NG0144:114: chen gyi sa la sa bcu rim gyis bgrod mi
NG0144:115: dgos te / da lta nyid nas rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dang mnyam par sangs rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NG0144:116: de'i phyir sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang 'di skad gsol to //
NG0144:117: tshogs kyi mchod pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NG0144:118: phung po mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NG0144:119: rig 'dzin sa la bde bar gnas //
NG0144:120: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kun mnyes te //
NG0144:121: byin gyi rlabs kyis dbang bskur nas //
NG0144:122: dngos grub dam par stsol bar mdzad //
NG0144:123: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med //
NG0144:124: ces sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs so //
NG0144:125: de la tshogs kyi mchod pa 'dis //
NG0144:126: yun ci tsam gyis 'grub ce na //
NG0144:127: rab kyis zla ba gcig nas 'grub //
NG0144:129: tha ma lo gsum tshun chad du //
NG0144:130: tshogs kyi mchod pa 'bul byas na //
NG0144:131: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NG0144:132: sangs rgyas byang chub thag mi ring *//
NG0144:134: tshogs phul ba'i yon tan ni /
NG0144:135: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir yang rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i zhal mthong bar 'gyur ba dang */
NG0144:136: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad sprin phung bzhin du gtibs te /
NG0144:137: ci bsgo ba'i bka' nyan cing */
NG0144:138: dngos grub kyi stongs dang grogs byed pas mthu dbang phun sum tshogs pa sbyin te /
NG0144:139: thams cad du bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa dang */
NG0144:140: longs spyod thams cad 'phel ba dang 'khor thams cad 'du zhing */
NG0144:141: nad dang duhkha mi 'byung zhing 'jig rten gyi lha
NG0144:142: ma srin thams cad kyang mnyes shing byin che bar
NG0144:143: mthong ba dang */ de la gar gyi spyi gtsug ltar len pa dang */
NG0144:144: sems can thams cad kyis kyang mig gi 'bru ltar mthong ngo *//
NG0144:145: yid du 'ongs shing dga' bar 'gyur ba dang */
NG0144:146: 'jig rten phyi mar rig 'dzin thams cad kyis mdun bsu ste /
NG0144:147: lcang lo can gyi gnas su phyin par 'gyur ro //
NG0144:148: tshogs ma phul ba'i skyon ni /
NG0144:149: bsgrubs kyang don med cing bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyang zhal 'dzum par mi mdzad cing */
NG0144:150: bsod nams dang skal ba'i skal ba chung ste dmyal
NG0144:151: ba dang yid dwags dang byol song gi gnas su
NG0144:154: tshogs phul ba'i phan yon dang ma phul ba'i skyon bstan pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NG0144:155: snyan cing yid du 'ong ba'i sgra sna tshogs dang
